Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry.
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 11
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: In this reimagining of Lewis Carroll's "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland," Tweedle Dee and Tweedle Dum compete for the love of the titular heroine.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF CLOVER: BLOODY TWINS
Author: QuinRose and Mamenosuke Fujimaru

Description: In this series, the son of a wine critic who must identify 12 wines in order to claim an inheritance.
Title: THE DROPS OF GOD, VOL. 4
Author: Tadashi Agi

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 40
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Yuma Tsukumo will stop at nothing to become the Duel Masters champion, but as a rank amateur, the odds are stacked against him. Luckily, he has a mysterious spirit named Astral to help him.
Title: YU-GI-OH! ZEXAL, VOL. 1
Author: Kazuki Takahashi, Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi
Contributor: by Kazuki Takahashi, Shin Yoshida and Naohito Miyoshi

Description: Welcome to Todo High, whose student body is composed of the toughest of brawlers.
Title: TENJO TENGE, VOL. 7
Author: Oh! Great Staff

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 41
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: From the publisher: "The campus culture festival is coming up for the students of Class 2-A." That means starting an all-girl band, despite the keyboardist being a boy.
Title: NEON GENESIS EVANGELION, VOL. 11
Author: Osamu Takahashi

Description: Naruto and his allies face off against a horde of ninja soldiers, some of whom are back from the dead and former friends.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 56
Author: Masashi Kishimoto
